{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":1,"day":30}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"伟大的变迁（朗诵诗）","authors":["王义俊"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史发展的长河中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年哟，仅是小小的浪花一闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而在中国现代史上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚过去的三年呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是一个伟大转折点——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难变成幸福！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严冬变成春天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！战斗了三年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攻下了多少堡垒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋涉了三年呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过了多少关山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——张开臂膀吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们热情地拥抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八○——这新的一年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在十年劫难的废墟上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉的成就象繁星灿灿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年的心血——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年的热汗——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国万象一新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地生机盎然！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实践告诉我们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有迈开大步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路才越走越宽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有荡平崎岖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能建造乐园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，过去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——那动乱的十年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已不满足弄镐使锨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在辽阔的大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们广开生产的门路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始了科学种田——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种着丰收的喜悦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌溉着富足的明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂矿的工人也在自己的岗位上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专心致志地生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻造富强的未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇铸自己的贡献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，科学家挣脱了满身锁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们可以大胆探索、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精心试验——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人类发掘科学宝藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为世界解答种种疑难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，文艺家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已踢开了“样板”的羁绊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们可以尽其所能，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酣畅、完美地进行表演，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭挞“四人帮”的罪恶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讴歌实现四化的明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史发展的长河中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年哟，仅是小小的浪花一闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而在中国现代史上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚过去的三年呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟带来如此伟大的变迁——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从乡村——到城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北国——到江南……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，战斗的三年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋涉的三年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它验证了党中央的英明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它展示了中华民族的才干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它呈现出安定团结的力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它预报着繁荣昌盛的明天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对这伟大的变迁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们应该怎样自豪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们应该怎样颂赞？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——让我们把新的一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装扮得更美丽些吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——用汗水浇出胜利的花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——用心血编制四化桂冠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用十倍的努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百倍的信心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让二○○○年那宏伟大厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早日耸立在我们面前！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}